nchronously.\n\nAlso retained the `LoadingTestCollectorTest` refinement intended to force the legacy cached class-literal path to execute.\n\nI did not run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_084e99528762e5290169f64dbbd7e881958d912ca39bc7461f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 603, "output": 1173, "cacheRead": 67072, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 68848, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777749416354, "responseId": "resp_084e99528762e5290169f64da90c488195bd7af0e71cbdea1f"}, "toolResults": []}
